OL,3,CWhat happens now Keir Starmer has
OL,4,Cresigned?
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has resigned as
OL,7,Fleader of the Labour Party, triggering
OL,8,Fa process to replace him not just as
OL,9,Fparty leader but also as prime
OL,10,Fminister.
OL,12,FHere, ITV News looks at what happens
OL,13,Fnext.
OL,15,FHow do candidates enter the contest?
OL,17,FCurrent Labour rules state that to
OL,18,Fmount a leadership contest, 20% of the
OL,19,Fparty's MPs ` or 81 colleagues ` need
OL,20,Fto back a candidate first.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
