OL,3,CWhat happens now Keir Starmer has
OL,4,Cresigned?
OL,6,FWho could stand in a contest?
OL,8,FAndy Burnham's return to Westminster
OL,9,Fafter winning the Makerfield by-
OL,10,Felection last week has put him front
OL,11,Fand centre of this race.
OL,13,FAllies of Burnham have already said he
OL,14,Fhas the required number of MPs to
OL,15,Fstand, and throughout his campaign to
OL,16,Fbecome an MP, he frequently commented
OL,17,Fon the change he plans to deliver on a
OL,18,Fnational stage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
