OL,3,CWhat happens now Keir Starmer has
OL,4,Cresigned?
OL,6,FFormer Health Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,7,Fhad previously said he would have the
OL,8,Fbacking, but on Monday said he
OL,9,Fsupports Burnham instead.
OL,11,FIn a letter posted on X, Streeting
OL,12,Fsaid "we can roll up our sleeves and
OL,13,Fhelp him deliver the change" as he
OL,14,Fendorsed the former Mayor for the
OL,15,Fleadership.
OL,17,FOn Friday, it was reported that
OL,18,FStreeting may stand aside in the
OL,19,Fcompetition in return for a cabinet
OL,20,Frole.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
