OL,3,CWhat happens now Keir Starmer has
OL,4,Cresigned?
OL,6,FFormer Royal Marines officer Al Carns,
OL,7,Fwho quit as armed forces minister in a
OL,8,Frow over defence funding and the
OL,9,Ftreatment of Northern Ireland
OL,10,Fveterans, has also hinted he would
OL,11,Fseek to enter a leadership race,
OL,12,Falthough it is unclear whether the MP
OL,13,F` who was only elected in 2024 ` has
OL,14,Fthe supporters required to get on the
OL,15,Fballot paper.
