OL,3,CWhat happens now Keir Starmer has
OL,4,Cresigned?
OL,6,FHow would a Labour leadership contest
OL,7,Fwork?
OL,9,FAfter a leadership hopeful nails down
OL,10,F81 backers in the Commons and support
OL,11,Ffrom constituency parties and trade
OL,12,Funions, candidates are then put to a
OL,13,Fvote among party members, who rank
OL,14,Fthem in order of preference.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
