OL,3,CWhat happens now Keir Starmer has
OL,4,Cresigned?
OL,6,FThere will likely be hustings for MPs
OL,7,Fduring this time to allow candidates
OL,8,Fto defend their policies.
OL,10,FThe plan would be that a new leader is
OL,11,Fin place before parliament returns on
OL,12,FSeptember 1 to allow candidates time
OL,13,Fto prepare for a contest and their
OL,14,Fpotential plan for government.
OL,16,FIf there is no contest as only one
OL,17,Fcandidate stands, then they would
OL,18,Fexpect to be in place by July 17 or 18.
OL,20,FWho gets to vote?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
