OL,3,CWhat happens now Keir Starmer has
OL,4,Cresigned?
OL,6,FThe decision-making rests with party
OL,7,Fmembers and affiliated trade union
OL,8,Fsupporters, even though the party
OL,9,Fleader will become the UK's prime
OL,10,Fminister.
OL,12,FThe voters rank each candidate in
OL,13,Forder of preference, and if a
OL,14,Fcandidate secures over 50% of the
OL,15,Ffirst preference votes, they are
OL,16,Fdeclared the winner and will become
OL,17,Fthe new leader of the Labour Party, or
OL,18,Fin Starmer's case, remain in his job.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
