OL,3,CWhat happens now Keir Starmer has
OL,4,Cresigned?
OL,6,FBurnham's significant support among
OL,7,Fthe parliamentary party could mean he
OL,8,Fends up as the only candidate.
OL,10,FWith no need for a membership ballot,
OL,11,Fthat scenario could see the contest
OL,12,Fwrapped up within a matter of weeks or
OL,13,Feven days.
OL,15,FBut given Burnham's apparent
OL,16,Fpreference for a three-month
OL,17,F"transition" period to allow him to
OL,18,Fprepare for government, it is unclear
OL,19,Fwhat would happen next in the event he
OL,20,Fwere the only candidate.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
