OL,3,CWhat happens now Keir Starmer has
OL,4,Cresigned?
OL,6,FThis transition period would leave
OL,7,FStarmer as a lame duck over a period,
OL,8,Fincluding a Nato summit where
OL,9,Fcountries are expected to set out
OL,10,Fplans to increase defence spending,
OL,11,Fand a UK-EU summit in Brussels seen as
OL,12,Fcrucial to Labour's attempts to reset
OL,13,Frelations with the bloc.
OL,15,FThere is some precedent for such a
OL,16,Fcoronation, however.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
