OL,3,CWhat happens now Keir Starmer has
OL,4,Cresigned?
OL,6,FGordon Brown was the only candidate to
OL,7,Freceive enough nominations in Labour's
OL,8,F2007 leadership election more than a
OL,9,Fmonth before Tony Blair formally
OL,10,Fstepped down as prime minister.
OL,12,FIn that period, Brown still attended
OL,13,Fleadership hustings around the country
OL,14,Fto set out his ideas and attempt to
OL,15,Fwin over the public.
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
